---
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content';
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import FormattedDate from '../components/FormattedDate.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';

const entries = (await getCollection('blog'))
  .filter((post) => !post.data.draft && post.data.category === 'now-records')
  .sort((a, b) => b.data.pubDate.valueOf() - a.data.pubDate.valueOf());
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead
      title={`${SITE_TITLE} · Now Records`}
      description="Present-tense field notes from inside the 0.5 era: how AI, workflow, tools, and daily life are changing while the transition is still underway."
    />
    <style>
      .hero,
      .section,
      .card {
        padding: 1.35rem 1.45rem;
        border-radius: 22px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(var(--line), 0.8);
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.76);
        box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
      }
      .hero + .section,
      .section + .section,
      .section + .grid {
        margin-top: 1.2rem;
      }
      .eyebrow {
        margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
        color: rgb(var(--gray));
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
      }
      .lead {
        max-width: 46rem;
      }
      .muted {
        color: rgb(var(--gray));
      }
      .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 1rem;
      }
      .record-list {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        list-style: none;
      }
      .record-list li + li {
        margin-top: 1rem;
      }
      .record-list a {
        display: block;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
      }
      .record-title {
        margin: 0 0 0.35rem;
        font-size: 1.15rem;
      }
      .record-date {
        margin: 0 0 0.45rem;
        color: rgb(var(--gray));
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }
      .record-desc {
        margin: 0;
        color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
      }
      @media (max-width: 820px) {
        .grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <p class="eyebrow">Now Records / 当下记录</p>
        <h1>Field Notes From Inside the Transition / 从过渡现场内部留下的笔记</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          Now Records preserves the present tense as future source material. It is where the project
          records living workflow changes, AI collaboration, new frictions, new habits, and the feeling
          of working inside a historical transition before the period has settled into retrospective form.
        </p>
        <p class="muted">
          当下记录负责把“此刻还在发生的变化”保存成未来可回看的材料。它记录的是尚未沉淀成历史章节之前的
          工作流变化、AI 协作、新摩擦、新习惯，以及身处过渡现场时真实的感受和判断。
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="grid">
        <article class="section">
          <h2>What belongs here / 这里写什么</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Present-tense notes about tools, workflow, coordination, and daily work while change is still unfolding.</li>
            <li>Field observations that preserve atmosphere, rhythm, friction, and judgment before hindsight smooths them out.</li>
            <li>Grouped issues or single notes that are meant to remain discoverable as source material.</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
        <article class="section">
          <h2>How it differs from Open Volume / 它和开放卷的区别</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Now Records:</strong> present-tense witness material written from inside the ongoing transition.</li>
            <li><strong>Open Volume:</strong> chapter-shaped forward historical line for 2026+ material that may later be consolidated into a formal volume.</li>
            <li>When material is primarily observation and source capture, it belongs here. When it is already shaped like a historical chapter line, it belongs in the open volume.</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>Working rhythm / 工作节奏</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Now Records</strong> can publish as single notes or grouped issues whenever the present needs to be preserved before it hardens into hindsight.</li>
          <li><strong>Open Volume</strong> collects chapter-shaped 2026+ material when the writing has already moved from witness notes toward a historical line.</li>
          <li>Material may move in one direction over time: present-tense note, then open-volume chapter line, then eventually a formal volume once the period boundary stabilizes.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>Published entries / 已发布条目</h2>
        <ul class="record-list">
          {entries.map((entry) => (
            <li>
              <article class="card">
                <a href={`/blog/${entry.id}/`}>
                  <h3 class="record-title">{entry.data.title}</h3>
                  <p class="record-date">
                    <FormattedDate date={entry.data.pubDate} />
                  </p>
                  <p class="record-desc">{entry.data.description}</p>
                </a>
              </article>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>Context links / 相关入口</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/volumes/vol-open-2026-2029/">Open Volume / 开放卷</a></li>
          <li><a href="/volumes/vol-4-2021-2025/">Volume IV / 第四卷</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog/2026-03-23-volume-roadmap/">Volume roadmap / 项目卷路线图</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
